headline: These Are 2 of the Worst-Performing Stocks in the S&P 500 in 2025
summary: The S&P 500 has rebounded to post a solid gain year to date.  Investors looking for bargains should consider the S&P 500's biggest laggards.  After briefly dipping into bear market territory just three months ago, the S&P 500 (SNPINDEX: ^GSPC) has quickly managed to recover, rising 6.6% year to date (as of this writing).

headline: Elevance Health Hit By Medicaid Troubles, Trims Outlook
summary: Elevance Health Inc. (NYSE:ELV) shares plummeted nearly 12% on Thursday after the health insurer reported second-quarter 2025 adjusted earnings that missed analyst expectations and significantly lowered its full-year guidance, overshadowing strong revenue growth.
